{"tid":750451,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實而家落黎香港果班同上一代落黎香港果班已經唔同哂","createTime":"2018-07-21T01:48:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-21T12:46:25.000Z","uid":113626,"like":18,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"ff33ae29014c54b130ab99bcd2e4b9ed0eb4419b","tid":750451,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T01:48:36.000Z","msg":"上一代, 係見住鄰國無得救, d人on99坐係到等死<br />\n不如成班黎香港博一鋪啦 (帶住資金同技術黎)<br />\n食住白人管治條水, 好快變成工廠地區靠出口貨品換取資金發展<br />\n而家, 鄰國正正有同一個工廠system (企左係香港1970年代果時)<br />\n只要你肯落手做一定唔會有事, 成個system只係punish d無生產力既人<br />\n你有生產力, 係內地屌後生女/買樓乜都做到<br />\n而家申請落黎香港果班150<br />\n尢其係果d大陸蝗婦走黎話好like港男然後呃哂佢地d $果班就係無生產力既表表姐<br />\n乜都唔想做, 想食公營system resource既人<br />\n根本d人心態都唔撚同哂啦, 你可以話以前d人都係咁樣落黎, 但成件事根本唔撚同 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25604b1f5dc358e7ee48fed5173c3e3e53f1d4b9","tid":750451,"uid":101390,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T01:54:12.000Z","msg":"根本就係<br />\n以前落黎嘅人係建設香港<br />\n97後落黎係搞破壞奪資源<br />\n邊有得比？"},{"pid":"30f0e3a0d7ecba9e893b868c1d772dc587cbc7e9","tid":750451,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T02:18:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"093d1dfdf9e2be865f44b95b46286ed725404b02","tid":750451,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T02:28:32.000Z","msg":"notebook巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45628061808a4998e898d6e9fd70dd039f2db141","tid":750451,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"093d1dfdf9e2be865f44b95b46286ed725404b02","tid":750451,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB